Description of incident: Dallas Fire-Rescue had several laptops containing patient information come up missing from several of their ambulances. "According to the city, those computers disappeared between January 1,  2011, and August 29, 2014. The city’s release did not say how many  laptops were unaccounted for — or how they disappeared. Messages have  been left for Sana Syed, the city’s spokesperson."No specific information was provided as to what information was in the files.
